      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Convert between V-Scale, Fontainebleau, and UK Tech grades instantly.
        <span class="block mt-2 text-lg opacity-80">Our unique tool accounts for gym vs outdoor grade differences, helping you understand your true climbing level.</span>
